193
00:18:51,343 --> 00:18:53,641
Senin de başına gelsin de
o zaman göreceğim seni ahbap.

194
00:18:53,679 --> 00:18:55,647
Eveet.

195
00:18:55,681 --> 00:18:58,013
Oh oh oh.

196
00:19:31,317 --> 00:19:34,218
